<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>마이페이지</title>
<style>
/* CSS 스타일링 */
body {
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	text-align: center;
	background-color: #f4f4f4;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
}

